LARDD 1
TITLE Driver Tools
TEXT Small helper tools for driver catalog maintainers.
SECTION Tools
ITEM mkdrfl.c -> host C tool that writes editable DRFL 2 driver-code files.
SECTION Example
ITEM cc mkdrfl.c -o mkdrfl
ITEM mkdrfl drv-rtl8139.drfl 10ec 8139 net rtl8139
ITEM mkdrfl drv-piix3ide.drfl 8086 7010 block ata-pio
END
